    4213 [label="SPDXLicense:\nRuby is disjunctively licensed project that allows the choice of this license\nand another. The other license choice has changed over time (from GPL\noriginally, to BSD-2-Clause currently), so one needs to be aware of that change.\nThe Ruby License itself is un-versioned, but has varied a bit over the years,\nthe last substantive variation being in 2002."
